---
---

<section id="precios" class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background glow effects -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-green-500/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] -z-10"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        Planes flexibles y escalables
      </h2>
      
      <div class="inline-block bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/30 px-6 py-3 rounded-full mb-8 max-w-full">
        <p class="text-green-400 font-medium flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm sm:text-base">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="hidden sm:block"><path d="M12 2v20"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
          <span class="block sm:inline">Desde $49/mes: menos que un día de sueldo, más clientes todos los días.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Elige el paquete de mensajes que mejor se adapte al volumen de tu negocio. Sin costos ocultos.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- Plan Básico -->
      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 to-transparent rounded-3xl opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition duration-300"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-[#0F1110] border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-3xl h-full flex flex-col hover:border-white/20 transition-colors duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Plan Básico</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6 h-10">Para negocios que quieren dejar de responder manualmente</p>
          
          <div class="flex items-end gap-1 mb-8">
            <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">$49</span>
            <span class="text-gray-400 mb-1">/mes</span>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-white/10 p-1 rounded-full text-white mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Hasta <strong>4,000</strong> mensajes/mes</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-white/10 p-1 rounded-full text-white mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Respuestas automáticas básicas</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-white/10 p-1 rounded-full text-white mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Mensaje de bienvenida + menú</span>
            </div>
             <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-white/10 p-1 rounded-full text-white mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Horarios automáticos</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-white/10 p-1 rounded-full text-white mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Panel de seguimiento</span>
            </div>
             <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-white/10 p-1 rounded-full text-white mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Soporte estándar</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a href="https://wa.me/51941300176?text=Hola,%20me%20interesa%20el%20Plan%20Básico" class="block w-full text-center bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300">
            Empezar ahora
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Plan Plus (Destacado) -->
      <div class="relative group transform md:-translate-y-4">
        <!-- Gradient glow -->
        <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-green-500 to-green-900 rounded-[2rem] opacity-75 blur-sm group-hover:opacity-100 transition duration-300"></div>
        
        <div class="relative bg-[#0F1110] p-8 rounded-[1.8rem] h-full flex flex-col ring-1 ring-green-500 shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(34,197,94,0.15)]">
          <!-- Badge -->
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-green-500 text-black text-xs font-bold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-bl-xl rounded-tr-[1.5rem] uppercase tracking-wider shadow-lg shadow-green-500/20">
            Recomendado
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-green-400 mb-2">Plan Plus</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-6 h-10">Para negocios que quieren vender más sin contratar personal</p>
          
          <div class="flex items-end gap-1 mb-8">
            <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-white">$79</span>
            <span class="text-gray-400 mb-1">/mes</span>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-green-500/20 p-1 rounded-full text-green-400 mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-white text-sm">Hasta <strong>8,000</strong> mensajes/mes</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-green-500/20 p-1 rounded-full text-green-400 mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-white text-sm">Flujos personalizados</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-green-500/20 p-1 rounded-full text-green-400 mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-white text-sm">Palabras clave y menús dinámicos</span>
            </div>
             <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-green-500/20 p-1 rounded-full text-green-400 mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-white text-sm">Configuración inicial incluida</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-green-500/20 p-1 rounded-full text-green-400 mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-white text-sm">Panel de seguimiento del servicio</span>
            </div>
             <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-green-500/20 p-1 rounded-full text-green-400 mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-white text-sm">Soporte prioritario</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a href="https://wa.me/51941300176?text=Hola,%20me%20interesa%20el%20Plan%20Plus" class="block w-full text-center bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-400 text-black font-bold px-6 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(34,197,94,0.4)] hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(34,197,94,0.6)] transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-[1.02]">
            Quiero automatizar mi WhatsApp
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Plan Pro -->
      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 to-transparent rounded-3xl opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition duration-300"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-[#0F1110] border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-3xl h-full flex flex-col hover:border-white/20 transition-colors duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Plan Pro</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6 h-10">Para negocios con alto volumen de clientes</p>
          
          <div class="flex items-end gap-1 mb-8">
            <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">$129</span>
            <span class="text-gray-400 mb-1">/mes</span>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-white/10 p-1 rounded-full text-white mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Hasta <strong>15,000</strong> mensajes/mes</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-white/10 p-1 rounded-full text-white mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Automatización avanzada 24/7</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-white/10 p-1 rounded-full text-white mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Validaciones y flujos complejos</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-white/10 p-1 rounded-full text-white mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Integración básica con CRM / formularios</span>
            </div>
             <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="bg-white/10 p-1 rounded-full text-white mt-0.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Soporte VIP</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a href="https://wa.me/51941300176?text=Hola,%20me%20interesa%20el%20Plan%20Pro" class="block w-full text-center bg-white text-black font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors duration-300">
            Quiero automatizar mi WhatsApp
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Demo Personalizada (Oculta/Secundaria) -->
    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
            ¿No estás seguro de cuál elegir? Solicita una <a href="https://wa.me/51941300176?text=Hola,%20me%20gustaría%20solicitar%20una%20Demo%20Personalizada" class="text-green-400 underline hover:text-green-300">Demo Personalizada (Solo por invitación)</a>.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">
        Cada plan incluye un límite mensual de mensajes. Al alcanzar el límite, el servicio se pausa o se cobra uso adicional previa coordinación.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
        El servicio utiliza WhatsApp Business API oficial.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Garantía -->
    <div class="mt-16 flex justify-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-4 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="bg-green-500/10 p-2 rounded-full text-green-500">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-left">
          <p class="text-white font-bold text-lg">Garantía de Satisfacción Total</p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Pruébalo por 7 días. Si no te convence, te devolvemos tu dinero.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
